Looking for a Co-Founder
text:
Hi, all I am looking for a cofounder who has deep technical background and has interest in creating a decentralized service. Specification: 1)Advanced proficiency in programming languages, such as C++, Java, and Python. 2)Extensive experience in back-end development, algorithms, and data structures. 3)Excellent communication and collaboration abilities.

I am hoping I can find some good engineers out here who are looking to work on a new startup.
